title: Top 30 Country March 18, 2014
description:
As the first week of Spring kicks off in the Northern Hemisphere we deliver Frankie Ballard his first number one single and welcome new entries from Jake Owen and Luke Bryan (who rises 15 huge spots from #44 last week).  Here are the top 30 U.S. Country singles according to Mediabase in crystal clear 320 kbps stereo for March 18, 2014.
